=version 1
=resource Costream Request
=method post
=endpoint /channels/costreams
=description Creates a new costreaming request.

include ../../_mixins.jade

p Hitting this endpoint causes a costreaming request to be sent out to various channels.

h3 Parameters

table.endpoint-param-table
    tr
        td.name from
        td.description Numeric channel ID which is making the costream request.
    tr
        td.name to
        td.description Array of numeric channel ID which you want the request sent to.


